response.overview: A brilliant and determined Briton, Nigel Mansell, has a season-long battle, not  only against the hard-charging Brazilian Ayrton Senna in the JPS Lotus but also  Keke 'Ten-tenths' Rosberg and the reigning World Champion Alain Prost in the  Marlboro McLarens as well as his Williams Judd Honda team-mate Nelson Piquet.  Features all 16 races accompanied by the sharp wit and informed narrative of TV  personality Clive James.
response.tagline: A review of the 1986 F1 season
response.title: FIA Formula One Season 1986
